Retrieve eval_data from object.

Retrieve eval_data from object.

eval_data(siamcat, errorIfNULL=TRUE)

# S4 method for ANY
eval_data(siamcat)

# S4 method for list
eval_data(siamcat)

Arguments

siamcat

(Required). An instance of siamcat-class that contains a eval_data..

Value

The eval_data list or NULL.

Examples

    data(siamcat_example)
    eval_data(siamcat_example)
